**/node_modules
**/.next
**/dist
**/.cache
**/*.tsbuildinfo
.git
.claude
old
data
*.log
# Note: `**/.turbo` intentionally NOT ignored. Turbo's cache directories are
# kept so the builder stage can warm Turbo's cache from the host (when
# available) and so the BuildKit cache mount on `pnpm run build` can persist
# `.turbo/` across builds (see Dockerfile builder stage).
